raw:
🏷️ **RAW PCM file size** (/notes #raw):

`filesize_in_bytes / second == channel * sample_rate * bit_depth / 8`

```| duration | filesize |
|----------|----------|
|       1M |   10.98M |
|       4M |   43.94M |
|      10M |  109.86M |
|       1H |  659.17M |
|       2H |    1.28G |
|       4H |    2.57G |```
